name: Listen in order to exist.
description:
When I decided to shut my mind, it revealed itself.
He was silent but disturbed my peace of mind.
I stopped controlling my body, my hands began to shake and my eyes to blink. Look for this non-thought to be able to listen to the wind, the sea, the birds, and life.
I did not achieve much with this dictatorial silence. It was only when I let my thoughts flow that I could begin to listen.
